 />\n4. 重推「租金管制法例」，籍此改變「中小企營商環境」和解決「劏房」問題。<br />\n5. 嚴格執行「競爭條例」，籍此改善貧富懸殊問題。<br />\n6. 利用兩制優勢，以中介人角色推動兩岸和平統一。<br />\n7. 即時全面取消小三TSA/BCA。<br />\n8. 委任建制和非建制派各不少於一名立法會議員加入行政會議。<br />\n9. 延續本屆政府未完工作，包括但不限於實施標準工時和取消強積金對沖機制。<br />\n10.選賢任能，當選後公開招聘管治團隊。"},{"pid":"d346e7999be175b55f85ad7d46b0c7e653620933","tid":111680,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">針對最新形勢分析：<br />\n<br />\n1. 林鄭月娥未夠601<br />\n2. 曾俊華形成威脅但係更加難夠601<br />\n3. 製造流選絕對係可操作最佳策略</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【邏輯推演】泛民選委應該同時提名胡國興葉劉淑儀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/88966/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/88966/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"a3c9f23bab4bbb6e7a62ce059b57aa0477d0b058","tid":111680,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"點解連登仔唔接受現實？係咪想學黃屍豬咁支持胡國興、曾俊華？"},{"pid":"1ddc7e481058f69aeb14e27d8f149106f54b9172","tid":111680,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"689都冇推23條呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ecf194e055c3b494ca9d48b39736ff95543545","tid":111680,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>689都冇推23條呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持 689！<br />\n<br />\n又焦土、又冇23條，仲有邊個好得過佢？"},{"pid":"3c471c4d12d19c5e3aaa8550fc5fdeb5838cc812","tid":111680,"uid":81037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:02:02.000Z","msg":"有有5個提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9e1ca617c90e02795214e2e149ed